Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:18.74,0:01:24.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,JULAI骑乘位\N特别篇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.35,0:01:27.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:27.55,0:01:29.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早安   请多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:29.82,0:01:30.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.29,0:01:34.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天很漂亮呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.42,0:01:39.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身体又变得更性感了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.83,0:01:41.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是错觉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.56,0:01:45.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在距离上次拍摄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.10,0:01:47.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过了多见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.51,0:01:55.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经过了半年了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.98,0:01:57.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.85,0:02:00.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个期间都没有拍摄吗\N是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.32,0:02:02.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有过什么有趣的拍摄吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.59,0:02:05.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有趣的拍摄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.19,0:02:11.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎没有呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.73,0:02:13.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.40,0:02:16.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此\N我还不大懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.07,0:02:18.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.60,0:02:28.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么让你比较兴奋的玩法呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.68,0:02:30.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我兴奋的玩法吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.55,0:02:33.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对   比较有感觉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.15,0:02:40.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拍摄不能由我决定\N有台词
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.82,0:02:41.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有剧I情发展
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.42,0:02:44.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然也很爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.56,0:02:48.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偶尔会私下做爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.57,0:02:55.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以当作私下做爱的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.24,0:03:00.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行的    对不起制作商\N不能那么自私
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.24,0:03:06.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有关系的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.45,0:03:08.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想听你说私生活的做爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.52,0:03:11.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一般都是正常位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.12,0:03:16.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样子久了也会厌倦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.19,0:03:20.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近喜欢骑乘位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.86,0:03:24.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,觉得这样子很爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.67,0:03:28.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己很爽    对方也很爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.94,0:03:34.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以觉得骑乘位比较好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.48,0:03:35.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骑乘位吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.08,0:03:40.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拍摄的时候有正常位有后入式\N还有很多体位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.75,0:03:45.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骑乘位也是其中的一部分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.35,0:03:52.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能长时间做一个姿势
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.63,0:03:54.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,觉得很可惜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.63,0:03:58.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说你想要长时间做吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.10,0:04:04.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你很诚实呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.31,0:04:07.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.84,0:04:09.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要骑乘位吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.71,0:04:11.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简单地说   是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.38,0:04:14.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骑乘位很兴奋吗\N是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.19,0:04:20.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.19,0:04:24.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎骑乘位可以让称更湿呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.06,0:04:26.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以让我如愿吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.13,0:04:31.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了   这次就如你所愿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.93,0:04:33.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.40,0:04:37.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天就特别地用骑乘位做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.14,0:04:39.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的可以吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.87,0:04:43.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然可以\N就坐在上面哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.41,0:04:45.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.82,0:04:47.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的   我做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.55,0:04:49.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不需要正常位吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.22,0:04:54.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男优应该不会想要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.82,0:04:58.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要的话再换吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.56,0:05:02.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然是以你为中心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.96,0:05:04.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.30,0:05:07.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么这次就特别地\N用骑乘位来做吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.90,0:05:10.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要做至肉棒断掉哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.17,0:05:13.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肉棒断掉吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.18,0:05:16.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,断掉的程度    不会断掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.58,0:05:18.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做到不能硬的程度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.51,0:05:20.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.39,0:05:26.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很厉害的肉棒哦\N是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.45,0:05:27.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不会断的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.06,0:05:29.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全没问题了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.46,0:05:34.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次是我们最厉害的肉棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.13,0:05:39.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那今天我要让他全部射出来\N做到无法工作的地步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.80,0:05:41.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让他不能和下一 个做爱\N是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.94,0:05:44.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请多指教\N请多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.47,0:05:47.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是厉害的肉棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.54,0:05:48.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.01,0:05:51.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要用骑乘位做吗\N可以吗
